{'text': '\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCyclin D1 cooperates with p21 to regulate TGFβ-mediated breast cancer cell migration and tumor local invasion\n\n\nSee discussions, stats, and author profiles for this publication at: https://www.researchgate.net/publication/240308294\n\nCyclin D1 cooperates with p21 to regulate TGFβ-mediated breast cancer cell\n\nmigration and tumor local invasion\n\nArticle\xa0\xa0in\xa0\xa0Breast Cancer Research · June 2013\n\nDOI: 10.1186/bcr3441\xa0·\xa0Source: PubMed\n\nCITATIONS\n\n84\nREADS\n\n249\n\n9 authors, including:\n\nSome of the authors of this publication are also working on these related projects:\n\nThe role of prolactin receptor signaling in breast cancer progression View project\n\nMeiou Dai\n\nMcGill University\n\n20 PUBLICATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0480 CITATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0\n\nSEE PROFILE\n\nAmal A Alodaini\n\nImam Abdul Rahman bin Faisal University\n\n6 PUBLICATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0238 CITATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0\n\nSEE PROFILE\n\nNadege Fils-Aime\n\nMcGill University\n\n8 PUBLICATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0209 CITATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0\n\nSEE PROFILE\n\nJimin Guo\n\nHarvard Medical School\n\n23 PUBLICATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa01,698 CITATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0\n\nSEE PROFILE\n\nAll content following this page was uploaded by Jean-Jacques Lebrun on 18 August 2014.\n\nThe user has requested enhancement of the downloaded file.\n\nhttps://www.researchgate.net/publication/240308294_Cyclin_D1_cooperates_with_p21_to_regulate_TGFb-mediated_breast_cancer_cell_migration_and_tumor_local_invasion?enrichId=rgreq-546f5489c023ee610eba64c346bbdf8a-XXX&enrichSource=Y292ZXJQYWdlOzI0MDMwODI5NDtBUzoxMzE1MTkxMDg2MjAyODhAMTQwODM2ODAwNzc1NQ%3D%3D&el=1_x_2&_esc=publicationCoverPdf\nhttps://www.researchgate.net/publication/240308294_Cyclin_D1_cooperates_with_p21_to_regulate_TGFb-mediated_breast_cancer_cell_migration_and_tumor_local_invasion?enrichId